name: The Birds screenprint
description:
A3 size hand stencilled and screenprinted graphic. A montage of postwar vases and contemporary glass housing 3 seperate birds. Hand drawn illustration by Nylon.
Limited print run of 30, signed and numbered 2007.

name: Soda Pops.
description:
Candy coloured acid raindrops of Soda. Original mixed media painting on recycled wood. This piece is acrylic,enamels and aerosol paint and is varnished. Signed on the reverse 2007, one off and measures 14×10 inches.
Nylon has painted and illustrated for 22 years and clients include Playstation/Fosters beer/Granada TV/Mcarta/Dope clothing/Groovetech/Kazoo PR/Reebok..featured in Thames and Hudson books,Stencil Graffiti and Graffiti World as well as Garage magazine (Italy) Graphotism (UK) and Juice magazine (Germany)

name: Lucky 7
description:
Hand painted recycled skateboard deck,well worn texture and heavy gloss varnish. Features a skull and flames with pink dripping soda pops characters and lucky 7 dice,stars etc.
One off,signed by the artist on the reverse.
Other decks available.
